  "remarks": "QDe.132. Tehrik-e Taliban is based in the tribal areas along the Afghanistan/Pakistan border. Formed in 2007, its leader is Maulana Fazlullah (QDi.352). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020.; Listing: Listed by the 1267 Committee on 29 Jul. 2011 ( amended on 15 Jun. 2015, 24 Nov. 2020 )",
